    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;The audio layers of the MPEG-1 and MPEG-2 standards are in frequent use on the internet, but there is no uniform Multipurpose Internet Mail Extension (MIME) type for these files.  The intention of this document is to define the media type audio/mpeg to refer to this kind of contents. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
